column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.modelMag_u,p.g,p.modelMag_g,p.r,p.modelMag_r,p.i,p.modelMag_i,p.z,p.modelMag_z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = &&&
